sparql_query_kg2:
 Based on the provided information and the entity and relation mapping, here is the SPARQL query for DBpedia (KG2) to get all islands that belong to Japan:

```sparql
PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/>
PREFIX res: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/>

SELECT DISTINCT ?uri WHERE {
  ?uri rdf:type dbo:Island ;
       dbo:country res:Japan .
}
```

This query uses the mapped entities and relations from the Wikidata query to find all islands (`dbo:Island`) that belong to Japan (`res:Japan`) in the DBpedia knowledge graph.

